rComments: He is an amazing professor!! He tries to make sure everyone has the same opportunities by doing everything he can to ensure you get a good grade and you understand what you're doing. He tries to "be hip" so prepare for some lame jokes that have good intentions. Assignments are straightforward, lectures based off of textbook.

You have to download the revel app where the app is and he assigns readings and quizzes for it every single week. Also assigns essays here and there but makes it very clear what he wants in the essay. Can be a really tough grader (or maybe that's the TA)? Classes are weboption. Sometimes does activities in class to help students prepare for exams.

Have him for sociology. Amazing teachers, talk a bit too fast lol. Instructions for assignments are well clear. His lectures are depended on textbook. So no need to go to lecture if you end up reading the textbook.
